des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your BrizLabs Smart Christmas Lights, such as: Tree Lights. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “BrizLabs” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “BrizLabs” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “BrizLabs” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “BrizLabs” skill, and you'll be navigated to “BrizLabs” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the Christmas lights.”
“Alexa, turn off the Christmas lights.”
“Alexa, set the Christmas lights to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten Christmas lights to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim Christmas lights to 50%.”
"Alexa, set Christmas lights to green."
"Alexa, set Christmas lights to white."
